      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably preserved specimen, offered in a condition that can only be described as showroom-new. Meticulously curated and maintained to the most exacting standards, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. From the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, untouched interior, every detail confirms its collector-grade status. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of unrivaled integrity and mechanical perfection.",
