      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. Powered by the high-revving S65 V8, this unit features individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline, delivering linear power through a precision-shifted 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains impeccably rigid, complemented by the factory carbon-fiber roof and Electronic Damper Control (EDC). Maintenance is comprehensive, with recent rod bearing replacement and subframe reinforcement performed as preventative measures. The Alpine White finish is factory-correct with zero imperfections, and the interior retains its showroom-fresh matte texture. This is a turn-key, investment-grade example of the final atmospheric M-car.",
